Based on instructor replies in each respective Piazza: Yes but be consistent for 188 and yes in general but not the first week for 177

If you are enrolled, then the Options option should allow you to change sections.

Moving to the last place of the waitlist is what happens when you are waitlisted and you try to change sections (i.e. you drop the course and rewaitlist).

Can I attend any discussion I want?

For CS 188 there is an empty seat in the discussion I want to attend but I heard tons of horror stories people going to the last place of waitlist when they change discussion. How can I carefully change my discussion without doing something aweful?

I am enrolled in both classes (I'm not in waitlist) and am declared L&S CS.
